# Mission Control - Autonomous Agent Orchestration Platform

## Executive Summary

A purpose-built mission control for coordinating 5+ autonomous AI agents working on trading bots and full-stack applications. Built with Next.js, deployed on Vercel, with real-time agent status, task orchestration, and trading-specific controls.

---

